<p>(RECs)&nbsp;<strong>is a market-based instrument to promote renewable sources of energy&nbsp;</strong>and<strong>&nbsp;development of the market in electricity.</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>One REC is created when 1MWh<strong>&nbsp;of electricity</strong>&nbsp;is generated from an&nbsp;<strong>eligible renewable energy source</strong></li>
